### Additional Licensing Information for Audio Assets

The "Software" licensed above refers **exclusively** to the source code (e.g., HTML, CSS, JavaScript, React components).

This repository contains audio files in the `public/` and `src/assets/` directories that are original production music from Supercell's game, Brawl Stars, specifically from the 2025 Monthly Finals.

These audio files are **NOT** covered by the MIT License, and all underlying music, sound effects, and associated intellectual property remain the exclusive property of **Supercell**. 

These files are included for demonstrative and non-commercial purposes only, under Supercell's [Fan Content Policy](https://supercell.com/en/fan-content-policy/). No ownership of the music or audio files is claimed by the author of this repository.
